<title><![CDATA[我们总是老的太快/却聪明的太晚]]></title> 
<author>renjihe1988 &lt;admin@yourname.com&gt;</author>
<category><![CDATA[心灵鸡汤]]></category>
<pubDate>Fri, 10 Jun 2016 12:12:14 +0000</pubDate> 
<guid>http://i.renjihe.com/blog/read.php?7313</guid> 
<description>
<![CDATA[ 
	<span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">真心的对待换来的究竟是什么&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">是</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/shangxin/index1.html">伤心</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">是</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/nanguo/index1.html">难过</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">是</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/juewang/index1.html">绝望</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">更多的是对</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/wenzhang/aiqingwenzhang/">爱情</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">的质疑！&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">记得自己当初对别人说，不管曾经多么受伤还是要</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/xiangxin/index1.html">相信</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">有真爱存在！&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">可是当你一次次的受伤，一次次的被欺骗&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">你还能在对别人说要相信存在真爱吗？&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">真的很怀疑&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">终于你不在相信别人不再相信爱情不再相信真爱存在&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">太过为别人着想，最终受伤的只会是自己！&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">有些事你拼命地想忘记&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">却事与愿违的记得很清楚！&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/shanghai/index1.html">伤害</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">自己的是这个世上最愚蠢的的事&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">不管怎么受伤一定要记得爱自己&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">你可以</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/beishang/index1.html">悲伤</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">可以狠狠的哭，&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">但是记住之后要擦干</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/yanlei/index1.html">眼泪</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">面带</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/weixiao/index1.html">微笑</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">！&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">因为在这世上除了亲人没人会在乎你！&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">所以记得爱自己和亲人！&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">要想在这个</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/shehui/index1.html">社会</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">立足&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">就得经得起磨练、经得起敷衍，还要忍受得了尔虞我诈&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">要想活得</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/kaixin/index1.html">开心</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">就得变得没心没肺&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">经得起欺骗、经得起打击，还要受得了虚伪&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">一次次的打击之后&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">一定要懂得对任何事情都不要抱太多</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/xiwang/index1.html">希望</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">不然就会</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/shiwang/index1.html">失望</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">过多&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">自己想顺其自然的</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/wenzhang/shenghuosuibi/">生活</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">才发现顺其自然有多累&hellip;&hellip;&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">在这个世上，你不能要求别人对你像你对别人那样&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">你能做到的就是扮演好自己的角色&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来才知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">原来你拼命想忘掉的&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">就在不经意间被</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/shijian/index1.html">时间</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">渐渐的</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/yiwang/index1.html">遗忘</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">了&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">后来你也不知道&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">究竟是时间遗忘了你还是你遗忘了时间&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">席慕容曾经说过，&ldquo;遗忘是我们不可更改的宿命，所有的一切都像是没有对齐的图纸，从前的一切回不到过去，就这样慢慢延伸一点一点的错开来，也许错开了的东西，我们真的应该遗忘了。&rdquo;&nbsp;</span><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">既然我们回不到过去，那请你将过去遗忘。&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">潮起潮落，花开花谢，云卷云舒，不必记牢，&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">这样你又</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/yongyou/index1.html">拥有</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">了一颗轻盈的心，平静而且安宁。&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">有些事/无需记得&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">忘记一些伤痛，&nbsp;</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/kuaile/index1.html">快乐</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">就会多一些；&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">忘记一些凌乱的脚印，道路就会顺畅一些；&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">忘记一些成绩和荣耀，前行的脚步就会更快一些。&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">放开自己的心！这远远要比关紧心口要容易一些。&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">要知道，原谅，只不过是把事情悄悄地掩藏；&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">只有不记得了，才是深刻彻底的</span><a style="color: #333333; text-decoration: none; font-family: Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px" href="http://www.duwenzhang.com/huati/kuanrong/index1.html">宽容</a><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; font-family: Simsun">。</span>
